<div>
	<p> A password is considered valid if all the following constraints are satisfied:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>It contains at least 8 characters and at most 20 characters.</li>
		<li>It contains at least one digit.</li>
		<li>It contains at least one upper case alphabet.</li>
		<li>It contains at least one lower case alphabet.</li>
		<li>It contains at least one special character which includes <strong>!@#$%&*()-+=^</strong>.
		</li>
		<li>It doesn&#39;t contain any white space.</li>
	</ul>
</div>